dend

Class Vertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • dend.Vertex

  • public class Vertex
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a vertex or node in a graph. Modified based on Vertex.java of the ImageJ AnalyzeSkeleton_ plugin by Ignacio Arganda-Carreras.

    For more information about the original plugin, visit the AnalyzeSkeleton home page: http://fiji.sc/AnalyzeSkeleton

    Author:
    Diana Bank, Elena Zhong, Chun Han Lab, Cornell University
